<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="ISO-8859-1">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="./assets/images/favicon.png">
<title>[PSG Registrar Robo]</title>
<style>
	input[type=submit] {
	  background-color: #04AA6D;
	  border: none;
	  color: white;
	  padding: 6px 14px;
